resources.residEmptySourceMessage_EmptySourceView: Nëbbees na mboolem sa balluwaayi nataal. Ngir wone yeneen, soppil say jekkal.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_GenericDevice:
Jëfekaayu Nataal moo lay won nataal ak wideo yu bawoo ci mboolem say jumtukaay ci benn barab.

Ngir gise nataal ak wideo yi ci beneen PC, demal ca PC booba, dugge fa ci SkyDrive.com/windows ngir yebbi te samp fa Microsoft SkyDrive, teg ci, dugge ak sa sàqum Microsoft te nga jëljekkalu Jote say taxañ fépp.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_Device: Bu dee am nga ci benn, na wóor ne def nga léen ci kàggu Nataal yi bu {{%1}}.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_SkyDrive:
SkyDrive moo lay may dencuwaayu nataal, wideo ak wayndare bu amul fay, bu ko defee nga man cee jote foo man a nekk.

Demal SkyDrive.com ngir tàmbali. Bépp nataal mbaa wideo boo fa denc dees na ko wone fii.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_PicturesLibrary:
Ngir tàmbali, lonkal ab jumtukaay (jëfekaay, telefon, dawalukaayu USB, añs.), teg ci jëli mbaa duppi ay nataal aki wideo yi sa Kàggu Nataal.

Bu fekkee nga xës ame ay nataal aki wideo ci PC bii, wérlul ni ñoongi ci sa Kàggu Nataal. Man ngaa saytoo sa Kàggu Nataal ci Wërukaayu Taxañ.
